
Situation:

I've been hired as a Data Analyst for the Taste of the World Cafe, a restaurant that has 
diverse menu offerings and serves generous portions.

Assignment:

I've been asked to dig into the customer data to see which menu items are doing well, not well and
what the top customers seem to like the best.

Objectives:

Explore the menu table to get an idea of what's on the new menu.
Explore the orders table to get an idea of the data that's been collected.
Use both tables to understand how customers are reacting to the new menu.

SOURCE:  Maven Analytics (Guided Projects)
URL:   https://mavenanalytics.io/


